The four best words I've used to start are

Pound
Might
Brews
Flack

They use every letter but q,y,z,x,v, and j.

If there's 4 letters with a u, you might need q. If there's 3 or 4, it's likely a repeat letter or a y at end. X, z, and v words are noticeable. J is rare.

@gigi_rivera71 I do that to. But because quordle does so many weird words, like radii, I tend to use 4 words and not duplicate letters for the first 4. I vary the words but usually about 10 words I'll mix. Then I can only make one mistake or lose.
